{"title":"Tectonica Intubacion iPad","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/UCI-Medicina Crítica/Tectonica Intubacion iPad.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Tectónica de\\NIntubación","guid":"herFptyHrq1teKy-uQ3pHA","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"PREPARACIÓN","guid":"","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Evaluación vía\\Naérea difícil","guid":"vQ4zKpibc__dUm1hFVPrAA","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"LEMON: Look, Evaluate 3-3-2, Mallampati, Obstruction, Neck","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"Mallampati I-IV → predictor visualización glótica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"2","text":"Apertura bucal ‹3 cm → DIFÍCIL","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"2","text":"Distancia tiromentoniana ‹6 cm → DIFÍCIL","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"2","text":"Cuello: movilidad, circunferencia, traqueotomía previa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"2","text":"CFS ≥5 → AM FRÁGIL → mayor riesgo complicaciones","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"9","parent":"1","text":"Personal\\Ny roles","guid":"RrxSGjYWEmt0zMEzsCtDsQ","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"Operador principal (laringoscopista)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"9","text":"Asistente 1 → maniobras externas (BURP), presión cricoides","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"9","text":"Asistente 2 → medicamentos, monitorización","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"9","text":"Time-out previo → CHECKLIST OBLIGATORIO","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"14","parent":"1","text":"Checklist\\Npre-intubación","guid":"VldF_iuirXQBNP6737IL7w","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"Monitorización: ECG, SpO2, ETCO2, PA invasiva si disponible","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"14","text":"Acceso venoso ≥2 vías","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"14","text":"Aspiración funcionando → punta Yankauer al alcance","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"14","text":"Material: laringoscopio + videolaringoscopio, hoja adecuada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"14","text":"Tubo endotraqueal: diámetro correcto + cuff verificado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"14","text":"Guía/bougie preparado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"14","text":"Bolsa-mascarilla funcional + O2 conectado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"14","text":"Medicamentos preparados y listos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"14","text":"Posición cama: 90° si posible (anti-Trendelenburg)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"24","parent":"0","text":"PREOXIGENACIÓN","guid":"","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"Objetivo SpO2 ≥95% (idealmente 100%) previo a apnea","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"24","text":"Técnicas según\\Ndisponibilidad","guid":"nJtziLmdKNYf_5di8XQzAA","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"Mascarilla facial 15 L/min → 3-5 min o 8 respiraciones CV","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"HFNC (OAF) 40-60 L/min FiO2 100%\\N→ SUPERIOR en IRAH","guid":"0BeaxpN8CiXVhDL_TKzAmA","children":[{"id":"29","parent":"28","text":"Estudio FLORALI → menor mortalidad 90 días (12 vs 23-28%)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"28","text":"Continuar durante laringoscopia → oxigenación apneica","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"31","parent":"26","text":"VNI 5-10 min previo → en IRAH hipoxémica severa","guid":"","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"PRECAUCIÓN: no retrasar intubación, riesgo VILI","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"33","parent":"26","text":"RAM (posición rampa) → 25° en obesos → ↑ tiempo apnea segura","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"34","parent":"24","text":"Tiempo de\\Napnea segura","guid":"WDSz0UOfy2clZ48B0AC9Dg","children":[{"id":"35","parent":"34","text":"Adulto sano: ~8 min","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"34","text":"AM frágil/desnutrido/EPOC: ‹3 min → URGENCIA preoxigenación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"34","text":"Obeso: ‹2-3 min","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"38","parent":"24","text":"Oxigenación\\Napneica","guid":"yZ51xtA7cgYDacHoK0WaRQ","children":[{"id":"39","parent":"38","text":"HFNC 15 L/min nasal O2 durante laringoscopia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"38","text":"↓ desaturación en intentos prolongados","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"38","text":"Checklist use → desaturación 2% vs 22.2% sin checklist (p‹0.001)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"42","parent":"0","text":"FARMACOLOGÍA\\N(RSI)","guid":"nPHEaFGGLL-FHKwur6Ba6Q","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"Secuencia Rápida de Intubación → estándar UCI/Urgencias","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"42","text":"Inductor\\N(hipnótico)","guid":"A9g4jM1E4CkdYf9B36ubHg","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"KETAMINA 1-2 mg/kg IV →\\NPRIMERA LÍNEA en UCI","guid":"GLMlREsKJkFXempHeugCtw","children":[{"id":"46","parent":"45","text":"Ventajas: broncodilatador, estabilidad hemodinámica","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"45","text":"AM: 1 mg/kg → evitar dosis plenas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"45","text":"Precaución: ↑ presión intracraneal controvertido","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"49","parent":"44","text":"Propofol 1.5-2 mg/kg → solo paciente\\Nhemodinámicamente ESTABLE","guid":"rkw3Yn17exQsEcef85z3vQ","children":[{"id":"50","parent":"49","text":"AM: 0.5-1 mg/kg → riesgo hipotensión severa","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"49","text":"↓ dosis en hipoalbuminemia (unión proteica alterada)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"52","parent":"44","text":"Etomidato 0.3 mg/kg → alternativa hemodinámica","guid":"","children":[{"id":"53","parent":"52","text":"Supresión adrenal transitoria → precaución en sepsis","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"44","text":"Midazolam → EVITAR en AM → riesgo delirium, acumulación","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"55","parent":"42","text":"Bloqueador\\Nneuromuscular","guid":"5bjcaAhc42adZzOYN4ltOw","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"SUCCINILCOLINA 1.5 mg/kg →\\NPRIMERA LÍNEA RSI","guid":"bzm0E5LV0GZ94dhQV6le9g","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"Inicio: 45-60 seg, duración: 9-11 min","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"56","text":"CONTRAINDICACIONES: quemados, hiperpotasemia, miopatías","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"56","text":"AM: riesgo hiperpotasemia → cK elevada, inmovilidad","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"60","parent":"55","text":"ROCURONIO 1.2 mg/kg →\\Nalternativa si contraindicación SUC","guid":"Jydnd5hSVDPmH9sve-U79w","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"Inicio: 60-90 seg, duración: 30-60 min","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"60","text":"Reversión: sugammadex 16 mg/kg","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"60","text":"VENTAJA: reversión completa siempre disponible","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"64","parent":"42","text":"Analgesia\\Nadjunta","guid":"SUQbKX_T6RKnVxi5MxldqA","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"Fentanilo 1-3 mcg/kg → atenuar respuesta laríngea","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"64","text":"Lidocaína 1.5 mg/kg → indicación controvertida (HTE)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"67","parent":"42","text":"Hipotensión\\Npost-intubación","guid":"EH4D4OJFitjqeLxe_QZ0Nw","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"Frecuente en AM (~10-15%) → ANTICIPA y prepara vasopresores","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"67","text":"Norepinefrina lista en jeringa: 0.1 mcg/kg/min inicio","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"67","text":"Causas: vasodilatación inductores, ↑ presión intratorácica, hipovolemia","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"71","parent":"0","text":"POSICIONAMIENTO","guid":"","children":[{"id":"72","parent":"71","text":"Posición olfateo\\N(sniffing position)","guid":"CIWnWMk3jmZaiuMDjtXCsQ","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"Flexión cervical + extensión atlanto-occipital","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"72","text":"Alinea ejes oral-faríngeo-laríngeo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"72","text":"Mejoría visualización Cormack-Lehane","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"76","parent":"71","text":"Rampa (ramp position)\\Nen obeso/AM","guid":"sG3WVtJ7Kf1jzHARd-HZ0Q","children":[{"id":"77","parent":"76","text":"Cabeza y tórax superior elevados 20-30°","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"76","text":"Meato auditivo externo a nivel del esternón","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"76","text":"↑ tiempo apnea segura, mejor visualización","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"80","parent":"71","text":"Colchoneta de rampa o sábanas enrolladas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"71","text":"Anti-Trendelenburg (30°) → ↓ aspiración, ↑ FRC","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"82","parent":"0","text":"LARINGOSCOPIA","guid":"","children":[{"id":"83","parent":"82","text":"Laringoscopia directa (LD) vs\\Nvideolaringoscopia (VL)","guid":"5bPhA9w33yzk_pk945b0Lg","children":[{"id":"84","parent":"83","text":"VL → RECOMENDADA como primera línea en UCI","guid":"","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"FPS LD: 72.9% vs VL: 88.2% (p‹0.001) → Grant et al, 2021","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"84","text":"Especialmente útil en vía aérea difícil predicha","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"84","text":"Videolaringoscopio con canal → permite tubo guiado","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"88","parent":"83","text":"LD → útil en entrenamiento, técnica de respaldo","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"89","parent":"82","text":"Hojas\\Ndisponibles","guid":"W7kySxoi4SmAx--En0Odiw","children":[{"id":"90","parent":"89","text":"Macintosh (curva) → vallécula → eleva epiglotis indirectamente","guid":"1JzaabfuLZnhXrtWOB-SpQ","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"89","text":"Miller (recta) → eleva epiglotis directamente → mejor en apertura limitada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"89","text":"Hoja hiperangulada (VL) → ángulo 60-90° → difícil dirección tubo → usar bougie","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"93","parent":"82","text":"Técnica de\\Nlaringoscopia","guid":"upbQ7vjTYXKnj8zLdtRmxw","children":[{"id":"94","parent":"93","text":"Apertura bucal → tijera (pulgar-índice), evitar palanca","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"93","text":"Inserción línea media → barrer lengua a izquierda","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"93","text":"Avanzar hacia vallécula (Macintosh) → PUNTA VALLÉCULA asociada a ↑ FPS","guid":"","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"Miller KA, 2020: punta vallécula → aOR 7.2 (IC 95% 1.7-30.1)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"98","parent":"93","text":"Visualización glótica →\\NCormack-Lehane","guid":"tMq1JlNbzHWJn8OfAtSpkA","children":[{"id":"99","parent":"98","text":"I: cuerdas vocales visibles completamente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"98","text":"IIa: polo posterior visible","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"98","text":"IIb: solo aritenoide → FPS ↓ (aOR 6.1 para grado I-IIa vs IIb)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"98","text":"III: epiglotis solamente","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"98","text":"IV: nada visible","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"104","parent":"82","text":"Maniobras de\\Noptimización","guid":"tQEhXu5PtIgSNABtE_5cHw","children":[{"id":"105","parent":"104","text":"BURP → presión posterior-superior-derecha sobre cricoides","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"106","parent":"104","text":"HELP → elevación cabeza + tórax (Head-Elevated Laryngoscopy Position)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"104","text":"Tracción suave del labio comisura derecha","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"108","parent":"0","text":"INTUBACIÓN","guid":"","children":[{"id":"109","parent":"108","text":"Guía de intubación\\N(bougie/estilete)","guid":"dHu7Gj9rpUG_sFctyAoGLQ","children":[{"id":"110","parent":"109","text":"BOUGIE → ↑ FPS significativamente","guid":"","children":[{"id":"111","parent":"110","text":"FPS con bougie: 88.9% vs sin bougie: 73.0% (p‹0.001)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"110","text":"Indicado en Cormack-Lehane IIb-III","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"110","text":"Técnica: ángulo 30-45°, avanzar bajo epiglotis, sentir clicks traqueales","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"114","parent":"109","text":"Estilete rígido → pre-moldear con ángulo 35° en punta","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"115","parent":"108","text":"Técnica de\\Ninserción del\\NTET","guid":"nrZyndxHFQ6QVcdR2Ws5cg","children":[{"id":"116","parent":"115","text":"Visualización directa de cuerdas → NO insertar a ciegas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"115","text":"Tubo bajo visión, marcar profundidad (dientes: 21-23 cm ♂, 19-21 cm ♀)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"118","parent":"115","text":"Inflar cuff → presión 20-30 cmH2O","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"119","parent":"115","text":"VERIFICACIÓN\\NOBLIGATORIA\\NINMEDIATA","guid":"ZnXsq6m_MWe15M7Zp5BNVA","children":[{"id":"120","parent":"119","text":"Capnografía (ETCO2) → GOLD STANDARD → onda cuadrada CO2","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"119","text":"Auscultación bilateral + epigastrio","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"122","parent":"119","text":"Movimiento bilateral tórax","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"119","text":"SpO2 estable","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"119","text":"Rx tórax → posición final (carina + 2-3 cm)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"125","parent":"108","text":"Fijación","guid":"","children":[{"id":"126","parent":"125","text":"Cinta adhesiva o dispositivo comercial","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"125","text":"Marcar nivel en dientes/encías","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"125","text":"Proteger con tela si piel frágil (AM → riesgo lesión piel)","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"129","parent":"0","text":"VÍA AÉREA\\NDIFÍCIL","guid":"KrWNn-1edpsIhUwca5BlXw","children":[{"id":"130","parent":"129","text":"Algoritmo vía aérea difícil\\N(DAS/ASA/SIAARTI)","guid":"4h-QiPnNTpH9ZpHXnNh8FA","children":[{"id":"131","parent":"130","text":"PLAN A → técnica primaria (VL/LD)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"132","parent":"130","text":"PLAN B → alternativa (cambio hoja, bougie, posición)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"130","text":"PLAN C → oxigenación de emergencia (mascarilla, LMA)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"130","text":"PLAN D → vía aérea quirúrgica (cricotirotomía)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"135","parent":"129","text":"Dispositivos supraglóticos\\N(LMA/i-gel)","guid":"z83yXWyFR7As4yzdeP7tjg","children":[{"id":"136","parent":"135","text":"PUENTE hasta vía aérea definitiva","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"135","text":"LMA Fastrach → permite intubación a través","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"135","text":"i-gel → inserción rápida, sin manguito inflable","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"139","parent":"129","text":"Cricotirotomía de\\Nemergencia","guid":"9eC6_9R9Ue764aCez75UIw","children":[{"id":"140","parent":"139","text":"CANT INTUBATE CANT OXYGENATE → DECISIÓN INMEDIATA","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"139","text":"Técnica quirúrgica vs dilatacional (Seldinger)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"139","text":"Membrana cricotiroidea → palpación (2 cm bajo cartílago tiroides)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"139","text":"AM: anatomía puede ser difícil → calcificación cartílagos","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"144","parent":"129","text":"Intubación con fibroscopio\\N(vigil/nasal)","guid":"b-FadtVcRszocg7KEt_n6g","children":[{"id":"145","parent":"144","text":"Vía aérea difícil predicha + paciente colaborador","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"144","text":"Anestesia tópica: lidocaína nebulizada + spray","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"144","text":"Tiempo: 5-10 min → PLANIFICAR con antelación","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"148","parent":"0","text":"CONSIDERACIONES\\NGERIÁTRICAS","guid":"GH-WxUTPXSvZx0mG9ZwevA","children":[{"id":"149","parent":"148","text":"Anatomía\\Nalterada","guid":"AJ1nelqrHlFr9o1id-fZTw","children":[{"id":"150","parent":"149","text":"Dentición: prótesis → RETIRAR antes, dientes sueltos → DOCUMENTAR","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"149","text":"Apertura bucal limitada → ATM artritis/rigidez","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"149","text":"Osteoporosis cervical → CUIDADO extensión cuello → lesión C1-C2","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"149","text":"Calcificación cartílago cricoide → dificultad cricotirotomía","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"154","parent":"148","text":"Fisiología\\Ndesfavorable","guid":"IFhu40EgJTqjLw5E5tPGuw","children":[{"id":"155","parent":"154","text":"Reserva funcional ↓ → tiempo apnea segura BREVE","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"154","text":"Sarcopenia diafragmática → reclutamiento lento post-extubación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"154","text":"↓ depuración renal/hepática → duración BNM prolongada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"154","text":"Reflejo tusígeno ↓ → mayor riesgo aspiración","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"159","parent":"148","text":"Farmacocinética","guid":"","children":[{"id":"160","parent":"159","text":"Volumen distribución ↓ → dosis inductores ↓ 30-50%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"159","text":"Unión proteica ↓ (hipoalbuminemia) → ↑ fracción libre","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"162","parent":"159","text":"Propofol → RIESGO HIPOTENSIÓN SEVERA → EVITAR en AM inestable","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"159","text":"Ketamina → primera elección en AM con inestabilidad","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"159","text":"Succinilcolina → vigilar K+ (inmovilidad, sarcopenia)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"159","text":"Rocuronio → metabolismo hepático: ↑ t½ en hepatopatía","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"166","parent":"148","text":"Complicaciones\\Nincrementadas","guid":"aXSXCeV4NwpH2DlZomTHXw","children":[{"id":"167","parent":"166","text":"Hipotensión post-intubación → mayor frecuencia AM","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"166","text":"Broncoaspiración → reflujo + reflejo deglutorio ↓","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"166","text":"Daño dental/labial → piel y mucosa frágil","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"170","parent":"166","text":"Delirium post-procedimiento → sedación mínima, orientar siempre","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"166","text":"Proporcionalidad terapéutica\\N→ EVALUAR ANTES","guid":"htCFbPbXgaDONJ7sHUtGzw","children":[{"id":"172","parent":"171","text":"CFS ≥7 → discutir objetivos de cuidado con familia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"171","text":"IOT NO es obligatoria si va en contra de voluntades del paciente","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"174","parent":"0","text":"Perlas Clínicas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"175","parent":"174","text":"VIDEOLARINGOSCOPIO primera línea en UCI → FPS 88.2% vs 72.9% LD","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"176","parent":"174","text":"BOUGIE siempre preparado → ↑ FPS 89% y ↓ desaturación","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"174","text":"CHECKLIST pre-IOT obligatorio → ↓ complicaciones (OR 0.39)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"174","text":"Oxigenación apneica (OAF nasal) durante laringoscopia → ↓ desaturación 2% vs 22%","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"174","text":"AM frágil: REDUCIR dosis de inductores 30-50% → ketamina > propofol","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"174","text":"ANTICIPA hipotensión post-IOT → norepinefrina lista antes de intubar","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"174","text":"Retirar prótesis dental SIEMPRE antes → riesgo aspiración","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"174","text":"EVALUAR proporcionalidad terapéutica antes de proceder en AM con CFS ≥7","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"174","text":"Succinilcolina: verificar K+ en AM inmovilizado → riesgo hiperpotasemia","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"174","text":"3 intentos máximo → al 3er intento → Plan C/D sin demora","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"185","parent":"0","text":"VER TAMBIÉN","guid":"","children":[{"id":"186","parent":"185","text":"→ Secuencia de Sedoanalgesia UCI (Farmacología)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"185","text":"→ Ventilación Mecánica Invasiva (UCI)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"185","text":"→ Vía Aérea Difícil (Procedimientos)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"185","text":"→ Delirium en UCI (Geriatría)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"190","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"","children":[{"id":"191","parent":"190","text":"1. Grant S et al. Safety of rapid sequence intubation in an emergency training network. Emerg Med Australas. 2021;33(5):857-867. doi:10.1111/1742-6723.13742","guid":"zwJmWU7g_OuOD863ZPtSSQ","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"190","text":"2. Miller KA et al. Technical factors associated with first-pass success during endotracheal intubation in children. Emerg Med J. 2020;38(2):125-131. doi:10.1136/emermed-2020-209700","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"193","parent":"190","text":"3. Vourc'h M et al. Preoxygenation in difficult airway management: PREOPTIDAM study. BMJ Open. 2019;9(4):e025909. doi:10.1136/bmjopen-2018-025909","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"194","parent":"190","text":"4. Frat JP et al. High-flow oxygen through nasal cannula in acute hypoxemic respiratory failure (FLORALI). N Engl J Med. 2015;372(23):2185-96.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"190","text":"5. Higgs A et al. Guidelines for the management of tracheal intubation in critically ill adults. Br J Anaesth. 2018;120(2):323-352.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"196","parent":"190","text":"6. Brown CA et al. Rapid sequence intubation for adults outside the operating room. UpToDate. 2024.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":196,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"UCI/Medicina Crítica","folder":"Entidades clínicas/UCI-Medicina Crítica","filename":"Tectonica Intubacion iPad","id":"map_2350","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"Tectonica Intubacion iPad"}